
## üß± Complex HTML Code (save as `shop.html`)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>My Online Shop</title>
  <style>
    .hidden { display: none; }
    .product { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px; margin: 10px; }
    .price { color: green; }
    .btn { background: blue; color: white; padding: 5px 10px; cursor: pointer; border: none; }
    .btn:hover { background: darkblue; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome to My Online Shop</h1>

  <div id="category-section">
    <h2>Categories</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#" data-cat="electronics">Electronics</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" data-cat="clothing">Clothing</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" data-cat="books">Books</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="product-list">
    <div class="product" data-id="p1">
      <h3 class="title">Wireless Mouse</h3>
      <p class="price">$25</p>
      <button class="btn add-to-cart" data-name="Wireless Mouse">Add to Cart</button>
    </div>

    <div class="product" data-id="p2">
      <h3 class="title">Noise Cancelling Headphones</h3>
      <p class="price">$99</p>
      <button class="btn add-to-cart" data-name="Noise Cancelling Headphones">Add to Cart</button>
    </div>

    <div class="product" data-id="p3">
      <h3 class="title">The Pragmatic Programmer</h3>
      <p class="price">$45</p>
      <button class="btn add-to-cart" data-name="The Pragmatic Programmer">Add to Cart</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="cart">
    <h2>Your Cart</h2>
    <ul id="cart-items"></ul>
  </div>

  <script>
    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.add-to-cart');
    buttons.forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const item = btn.getAttribute('data-name');
        const li = document.createElement('li');
        li.textContent = item;
        document.getElementById('cart-items').appendChild(li);
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
```

---

## üéØ Playwright Questions (Locator Practice)

 Question 1 ‚Äî Locate by Different Selectors

Write Playwright code to locate and print the text of:

1. The main heading (`Welcome to My Online Shop`)
2. The price of the second product (`Noise Cancelling Headphones`)
3. The "Add to Cart" button of ‚ÄúThe Pragmatic Programmer‚Äù
4. The category link for ‚ÄúClothing‚Äù


 Question 2 ‚Äî Locator Challenge

Find 3 different ways to locate the ‚ÄúAdd to Cart‚Äù button for the Noise Cancelling Headphones product.

